asset_contract.description:
Troverse Planets — the collection of 10,000 giant procedurally-generated Planets spread across the Galaxy 💎

⚠ Owner count may not be accurate on OpenSea due to the Staking feature launched on August 23 ⚠

The game allows the Planet owners to receive a portion of resources gathered and service fees paid by other players through their exclusive headquarters deployed on their planets.

[Troverse Dashboard & Staking Feature](https://dashboard.troverse.io/)

[Troverse Official Website](https://www.troverse.io/)

Troverse is an ever-rewarding galactic Metaverse of Play-and-Earn gaming where players Own, Explore, Collect, Trade, Compete and Earn in a massive open-world treasure hunting game, set in a galaxy of 10,000 planets, powered by Unreal Engine.

[Watch the trailer!](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vpWNqeiMdOk)

Follow us on: [Discord](https://discord.gg/troverse) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/TroverseNFT)
